  "1883370": {
    "name": "PEPPERED: an existential platformer",
    "steam_appid": 1883370,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《佩珀 PEPPERED》是一款探讨存在主义的平台跳跃游戏，你在游戏里的每一步选择都只有一次机会。<br>每个选择、每场头目战、每次失败，都会让剧情走向分叉，改变故事进展与最终结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/b940d7f3de01867bff9d7690cc9dc57a.poster.avif?t=1772197814\" width=616 height=333 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/b940d7f3de01867bff9d7690cc9dc57a.webm?t=1772197814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>剧情简介</strong><br><br>眼看末日将至，人们却无动于衷。一名办公室实习生决定亲自出手拯救世界。可这一举动却招来警察、吃瓜群众和媒体的联合挞伐，甚至还让他被扣上了“恐怖分子”的帽子。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/82036b0990a8624fbc4a62ce17ce5a94.poster.avif?t=1772197814\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/82036b0990a8624fbc4a62ce17ce5a94.webm?t=1772197814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色</strong><br><br>■ <strong>分支剧情</strong><br>游戏拥有多重结局与多条剧情路线。你每次失败或做出不同选择，都会影响剧情走向并引发大量分支......有时甚至会把你带到全新的区域，遇见新角色，或解锁全新的玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/9709cf3f97977d652b7d636394d5ca5c.poster.avif?t=1772197814\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/9709cf3f97977d652b7d636394d5ca5c.webm?t=1772197814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>■ 平台动作</strong><br>奔跑、跳跃、死亡，以及对着屏幕疯狂破防。<br><br>■ <strong>一次性首领战</strong><br>高难度首领战等你挑战。只要你输了，游戏不会让你读档重来……而是把失败当成既定事实继续推进剧情，并改写后续故事。<br><br>■ <strong>做出选择</strong><br>从对话回应到行动方式，都由你决定。这些选择会影响不同角色、当下事件的结果，甚至左右你的最终结局。<br><br>■ <strong>潜行关卡</strong><br>被当场抓住，悄悄溜过去，或找到隐藏解法都能通关。每个潜行关卡都有专属角色登场，你的选择将给他们带来不可逆的后果，外加一堆蠢得莫名其妙的爆笑场景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/bedd90a76067330bcebb537ff64d64e8.poster.avif?t=1772197814\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/bedd90a76067330bcebb537ff64d64e8.webm?t=1772197814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>■ <strong>探索世界</strong><br>踏入这个充满怪人和伤心人的诡异世界吧。和各有来头的NPC们聊天，翻看环境细节，或者干脆全都无视，由你决定。<br><br>■ <strong>一堆乱七八糟的破事</strong><br>也许你得推着购物车逃离追着你跑的小混混。又或者得老老实实填表格，或跟蹲在街角的疯子赌上几把。谁知道呢？（我知道。）<br><br>■ <strong>办公椅</strong><br>你能坐在上面转圈圈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/2f795e99abc5ffd11a43ebb2b2472a1a.poster.avif?t=1772197814\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1883370/extras/2f795e99abc5ffd11a43ebb2b2472a1a.webm?t=1772197814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
